                  },
                  {
                    "text": "{{date}}",
                    "style": "date"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "{{complainantName}}, herein referred to as the petitioner, represented by Advocate {{advocateName}}, respectfully submits as follows:",
                    "style": "bodyText"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "My client, {{partyName}}, {{partyType}}, hereby submits this application before this Honorable Court to request condonation of delay in filing my {{caseName}} numbered {{caseNumber}}. The delay was unintentional and occurred without any negligence on my part.",
                    "style": "bodyText"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "I sincerely apologize for the delay and assure this Honorable Court of my earnest efforts to rectify the oversight and proceed with the matter diligently. I assure this Honorable Court of my full cooperation and compliance with all procedural requirements going forward.",
                    "style": "bodyText"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "Reasons for Delay: {{{reasonForDelay}}}",
                    "style": "bodyText"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "The petitioner assures and undertakes to the Hon'ble Court that this request is made in good faith and will not prejudice the other party.",
                    "style": "bodyText"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "Prayer: {{prayer}}",
                    "style": "bodyText"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "{{{additionalComments}}}",
                    "style": "bodyText"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "Therefore, the petitioner humbly requests the Hon'ble Court to consider this application and grant permission for the condonation of delay in filing the aforementioned case/petition.",
                    "style": "bodyText"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "Dated this {{day}} day of {{month}}, {{year}}.",
                    "style": "date"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "{{advocateSignature}}",
                    "style": "advocateSignature"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "{{advocateName}}",
                    "style": "signature"
                  },
                  {
